### 1. Create a Draft Course (Allows missing fields for draft mode)
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/create
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": true,
  "courseTitle": "Fullstack Web Development with Node.js (Draft)",
  "shortdesc": "A basic draft of web developer course.",
  "enrollmentType": "Ongoing"
}


### 2. Create a Fully Published Course (All required fields provided)
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/create
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": false,
  "courseTitle": "Mastering Advanced Node.js 2026",
  "courseCategory": "647f1234567890abcdef1234",
  "shortdesc": "Become a backend master with advanced Node.js design patterns.",
  "longdesc": "This comprehensive course covers stream architectures, child processes, microservices, and cluster scalability.",
  "whatYouWillLearn": "Streams, clustering, child processes, multi-threading, security best practices",
  "posterImage": [
    "uploads/courses/nodejs_adv.jpg"
  ],
  "startDate": "2026-09-01T09:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2026-11-30T17:00:00.000Z",
  "totalSessions": 24,
  "timeZone": "UTC",
  "venueName": "Silicon Valley Coding Hub",
  "venueAddress": {
    "latitude": 37.774929,
    "longitude": -122.419416,
    "address": "456 Tech Parkway",
    "city": "San Francisco",
    "state": "CA",
    "country": "USA",
    "zipcode": "94103"
  },
  "batches": [
    {
      "batchName": "Weekend Morning Batch",
      "startTime": "09:00",
      "endTime": "13:00",
      "days": ["Sat", "Sun"],
      "seats": 30,
      "ReservedExternally": 5
    },
    {
      "batchName": "Weekday Evening Batch",
      "startTime": "18:30",
      "endTime": "21:30",
      "days": ["Mon", "Wed", "Fri"],
      "seats": 25,
      "ReservedExternally": 2
    }
  ],
  "price": 299.99,
  "refundPolicy": "7 Days Before",
  "enrollmentType": "fixedStart",
  "bookingCutOff": "2h"
}


### 3. Update a Course (Draft or Published)
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/edit/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseTitle": "Mastering Advanced Node.js 2026 (Updated)",
  "shortdesc": "Updated summary of backend development master class."
}


### 4. Publish a Draft Course (Transition from Draft to Published)
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/edit/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": false,
  "courseTitle": "Fullstack Web Development with Node.js",
  "courseCategory": "647f1234567890abcdef1234",
  "shortdesc": "Comprehensive fullstack coding boot camp.",
  "longdesc": "Learn HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.",
  "startDate": "2026-10-15T09:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2026-12-15T13:00:00.000Z",
  "totalSessions": 20,
  "timeZone": "UTC",
  "venueName": "Downtown Learning Hub",
  "venueAddress": {
    "latitude": 40.712776,
    "longitude": -74.005974,
    "address": "123 Broadway",
    "city": "New York",
    "state": "NY",
    "country": "USA",
    "zipcode": "10006"
  },
  "batches": [
    {
      "batchName": "Morning Intensive",
      "startTime": "09:00",
      "endTime": "13:00",
      "days": ["Mon", "Tue", "Wed", "Thu", "Fri"],
      "seats": 15
    }
  ],
  "price": 499.00,
  "enrollmentType": "Ongoing"
}


### 5. Invalid: Try to revert a published course back to draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/edit/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": true
}


### 6. Invalid: Try to set end date in the past
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/edit/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endDate": "2020-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}


#=========================================================FILTER==========================================================================

### 7. List Courses - Standard Retrieve (Active/Upcoming Courses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 8. List Courses - Filter by Status (Explicitly show Past courses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?status=Past
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 9. List Courses - Multi-way Filtering (Custom date range + Category + Search + Status combined)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?fromDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z&toDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z&categoryId=647f1234567890abcdef1234&search=Node&status=Upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 10. List Courses - Time Slot Presets (Happenings Soon, This Month, Today, This Weekend, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=happeningsoon,thismonth
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 11. List Courses - Time of Day Slot Filter (Morning, Afternoon, Evening)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?timeOfDay=morning,afternoon
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 12. List Courses - Geospatial Distance Search (Radius of 100km from Lat/Lng coordinates)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?latitude=37.774929&longitude=-122.419416&radius=100
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 13. List Courses - Viewport Bounding Box Map Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?north=37.850000&south=37.700000&east=-122.350000&west=-122.480000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14. List Courses - Organizer Courses (Latest Created First)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 15. List Courses - Organizer Courses Filtered by Ongoing Enrollment
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer,ongoing
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 16. List Courses - Organizer Courses Filtered by fixedStart Enrollment
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer,fixedstart
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 17. List Courses - Organizer Draft Courses Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer,draft
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 18. Retrieve Course Booking Cut-off Options
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/booking-cutoffs

